com.hazelcast.spi.merge

Interface SplitBrainMergeTypeProvider<T extends MergingValue>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the provided merging values, e.g. a simple MergingValue or a composition like MergingEntry & MergingHits & MergingLastAccessTime
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBasicConfig, AtomicLongConfig, AtomicReferenceConfig, CacheConfig, CacheConfigReadOnly, CacheSimpleConfig, CacheSimpleConfigReadOnly, CollectionConfig, ListConfig, ListConfigReadOnly, MapConfig, MapConfigReadOnly, MultiMapConfig, MultiMapConfigReadOnly, QueueConfig, QueueConfigReadOnly, ReplicatedMapConfig, RingbufferConfig, ScheduledExecutorConfig, SetConfig, SetConfigReadOnly

    public interface SplitBrainMergeTypeProvider<T extends MergingValue>
    Returns a class with the provided merge value types.

    Is implemented by config classes of split-brain capable data structures.

    Is used by the ConfigValidator to check if a data structure provides he required merge types of a configured SplitBrainMergePolicy.

    Since:
    3.10
